description:
This is a 24 minute workout called 'Beginner Zone 2 Cardio Workout - BODYWEIGHT/NO EQUIPMENT | 20 Minutes' from the channel Sunny Health & Fitness.
The workout falls under Cardio/Mat and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Looking to build your cardio base, strengthen your heart, and burn fat? Try this 20-minute Zone 2 Cardio Bodyweight workout designed by Sunny Trainer, James King III. Keep your body moving and your heart rate in Zone 2 by completing this workout a few times a week.

00:00 Warm Up: Start the workout with a warm-up to prepare your body for the exercises to come.

2:23 Arm Swings
Swing your arms back and forth to loosen up your shoulders.

2:49 Hip Circles 
Circle your hips in one direction, then switch to the other direction.

Workout : The main workout consists of 6 exercises that you will repeat 3 times. Each exercise lasts 30 seconds, and you'll have a 10-second break between each exercise.

3:27 Double Punch to Kickback 
Start with your feet shoulder-width apart and fists up by your chin. Punch out with both fists, then kick one leg back while punching with the opposite fist. Alternate sides with each rep.

3:50 High March 
March in place while lifting your knees as high as you can. ...
